### 2. **Text-Based Pipeline Example: TextClassificationPipeline**

**File:** `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775480940537-l66re4/src/pipelines.js` (Lines 218-331)

