   const pipe = await pipeline('image-text-to-text', 'HuggingFaceTB/SmolVLM-256M-Instruct');
   const out = await pipe('https://...some-image-url...', 'Describe this image.');
   console.log(out); // [{ generated_text: '...' }]
   ```

4. **Unit tests:** Run the test suite to validate the new test file is auto-discovered and
   passes:
   ```bash
   npm test -- --testPathPattern=pipelines
   ```
   Or specifically:
   ```bash
   npx jest tests/pipelines.test.js
   ```

